    body
        div.mdl-layout.mdl-js-layout
            div.mdl-layout__content.flex
                div.container.full-width.main.flex.flex-column
                    h1.text-center Генератор отмазок
                    div.result-wrap.flex-center.full-width
                        div.mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp.card-result
                            div.mdl-card__title.mdl-card--expand.flex-center
                                div#result.result Здесь будет отмазка
                            div.mdl-card__actions.mdl-card--border.flex-center.flex-column
                                div.mdl-textfield.mdl-js-textfield.mdl-textfield--floating-label
                                    input#name(type="text").mdl-textfield__input
                                    label(for="name").mdl-textfield__label Введите имя, от кого отмазываемся
                                button#go.mdl-button.mdl-js-button.mdl-button--raised.mdl-js-ripple-effect.mdl-button--accent.mdl-color--blue-800 Получить отмазку
                    footer.mdl-mini-footer.flex-center.text-center.full-width
                        div.mdl-mini-footer__left-section
                            ul.mdl-mini-footer__link-list.flex-column
                                li
                                    a(href="https://vk.com/public51016572")
                                        img.design-logo(src="build/img/design-logo.png")
                                li
                                    span.icon.icon-github
                                    a(href="https://github.com/littleguga/excuse-generator") Исходный код на github